Alma Tell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alma_Tell 0 Alma Tell (March 27, 1898 – December 29, 1937) was an American stage and motion picture actress whose career in cinema began in 1915 and lasted into the talkie era of the early 1930s.
